Package pacman.gameobjects

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GameObject
    Interface that is implemented by all in-game objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Blinky
    This class is responsible for managing the Blinky-ghosts.
    Clyde
    This class is responsible for managing the Clyde-ghost.
    Coordinate
    Coordinate is used by the Ghost-classes to find pacman and then deciding the direction where the ghost moves.
    Ghost
    The parent class of all ghosts that contains the needed methods for the ghosts' functions. e.g. getting the ghosts direction with a* -search algorithm.
    PacMan
    This class is responsible for PacMan.
    Pinky
    This class is responsible for managing the Pinky-ghost.
    Pointbubble
    This class contains the functions for the Pointbubbles.
    PowerPellet
    This class contains the functions of the Powerpellets.
    RandomDirection
    This class is used to set a ghosts direction randomly when PacMan is out of reach.
    Wall
    The class that manages the wall-objects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    Used by ghosts and pacman to move to a specified direction.
